              "text": {
                "content": "Authors look at formative assessment results and log data and use them as inputs for a RF model. REsults on data from 2 math courses shows that formative assessments, combined with previous summative assessments are good predictors of summative assessment and, moreover, better predictors than any form of student engagement. ",
                "link": null
              },
